PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1781010670
OL,3,CInquest finds teenage girl may not
OL,4,Chave drowned if warning signs were in
OL,5,Cplace
OL,7,FA teenage girl may not have drowned
OL,8,Foff the North Tyneside coast if there
OL,9,Fhad been adequate warning signs in
OL,10,Fplace at the location, an inquest has
OL,11,Ffound.
OL,13,FThirteen-year-old Edie Smart had been
OL,14,Fsat on some disused steps at the far
OL,15,Fend of the beach in Whitley Bay when a
OL,16,Flarge wave swept her into the sea,
OL,17,Fprompting a response by emergency
OL,18,Fservices on July 24, 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
