FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1781010670
OL,3,CInquest finds teenage girl may not
OL,4,Chave drowned if warning signs were in
OL,5,Cplace
OL,7,FAn inquest in Newcastle has been
OL,8,Fexploring what happened during the
OL,9,Fattempt to rescue Edie, as well as
OL,10,Fsafety at the scene.
OL,12,FSenior coroner Georgina Nolan said
OL,13,Fthere was no sign prohibiting entry to
OL,14,Fthe location and noted that Edie had
OL,15,Fclimbed through two sets of railings
OL,16,Fto access the steps, which were
OL,17,Fdescribed as "easily breached".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1781010670
OL,3,CInquest finds teenage girl may not
OL,4,Chave drowned if warning signs were in
OL,5,Cplace
OL,7,FShe said: "If a sign had been present
OL,8,FEdie would have taken heed. She would
OL,9,Fnot have entered the area or been
OL,10,Fwashed into the sea."
OL,12,FIn response, North Tyneside Council
OL,13,Ftold ITV Tyne Tees it accepts the
OL,14,Fcoroner's findings. A spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "We are deeply sorry for the
OL,16,Ffamily's loss and we offer our sincere
OL,17,Fcondolences to Edie's family.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1781010670
OL,3,CInquest finds teenage girl may not
OL,4,Chave drowned if warning signs were in
OL,5,Cplace
OL,7,F"Regular independent safety
OL,8,Finspections, both before and since
OL,9,FEdie's tragic death, found the
OL,10,Frailings to be safe, adequate and
OL,11,Fcompliant with British and European
OL,12,Fstandards, and this is the first
OL,13,Fincident of its kind at that location.
OL,15,F"In light of the coroner's verdict,
OL,16,Fthe local authority will urgently re-
OL,17,Fengage with the Royal Society for the
OL,18,FPrevention of Accidents to carry out a
OL,19,Ffurther review of safety measures in
OL,20,Fthe area."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1781010670
OL,3,CInquest finds teenage girl may not
OL,4,Chave drowned if warning signs were in
OL,5,Cplace
OL,7,FThe inquest heard the rescue was co-
OL,8,Fordinated by His Majesty's Coastguard,
OL,9,Fwhich included the option of sending
OL,10,Flifeguards who were stationed on the
OL,11,Fbeach.
OL,13,FMs Nolan said: "If the lifeguards had
OL,14,Fbeen called at the outset they would
OL,15,Fhave rescued Edie before she drowned."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
