OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1781010670
OL,3,CInquest finds teenage girl may not
OL,4,Chave drowned if warning signs were in
OL,5,Cplace
OL,7,FA Maritime and Coastguard Agency
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Our thoughts are
OL,9,Fwith everyone affected by the tragic
OL,10,Fevents at Whitley Bay, and we will
OL,11,Fcarefully consider the coroner's
OL,12,Fcomments. "
OL,14,FEarlier in the inquest, the Coastguard
OL,15,Fhad told the coroner that beach
OL,16,Flifeguards are not an automatic
OL,17,F"asset" as they have designated areas
OL,18,Fon the beach and also have to maintain
OL,19,Fsafety on the shore.
OL,26,@pD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1781010670
OL,3,CInquest finds teenage girl may not
OL,4,Chave drowned if warning signs were in
OL,5,Cplace
OL,7,FThe inquest heard earlier that Edie
OL,8,Fhad "never intended" to enter the
OL,9,Fwater that day and the conditions of
OL,10,Fthe sea made the rescue and life-
OL,11,Fsaving attempts extremely challenging.
OL,13,FToo upset to speak on camera, Edie's
OL,14,Ffamily read a statement at the
OL,15,Fconclusion. They said: "As we continue
OL,16,Fto come to terms with our loss, we
OL,17,Fwill now look to celebrate and cherish
OL,18,Fthe memories we have of Edie and
OL,19,Fimmense joy she brought to our lives."
OL,21,FHer death was recorded as an accident.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
